data.inputSetTemplateYaml:
pipeline:
  identifier: "NN"
  stages:
  - stage:
      identifier: "S2"
      type: "Deployment"
      spec:
        serviceConfig:
          serviceDefinition:
            type: "Kubernetes"
            spec:
              artifacts:
                primary:
                  type: "Ecr"
                  spec:
                    connectorRef: "<+input>"
                    imagePath: "<+input>"
                    region: "<+input>"
                    tag: "<+input>"
        infrastructure:
          infrastructureDefinition:
            type: "KubernetesDirect"
            spec:
              connectorRef: "<+input>"
              namespace: "<+input>"
